.TH btctax-reconcile-bulk-classify-inbound-income 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
bulk\-classify\-inbound\-income \- Bulk\-classify unknown\-basis inbound deposits as INCOME (mining|staking|interest|airdrop|reward): recognize MANY pending inbounds as ordinary income at their auto\-FMV (the daily\-close market value at receipt) in one confirmed batch, with a UNIFORM `\-\-kind` + `\-\-business` flag. Shows a preview surfacing the total income recognized + the count of inbounds EXCLUDED because no price was available for their date (those stay pending — an income row with no FMV would year\-gate). Each is a voidable decision; for a single deposit use `classify\-inbound\-income`
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbulk\-classify\-inbound\-income\fR <\fB\-\-kind\fR> [\fB\-\-business\fR] [\fB\-\-year\fR] [\fB\-\-from\fR] [\fB\-\-to\fR] [\fB\-\-wallet\fR] [\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-\-yes\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Bulk\-classify unknown\-basis inbound deposits as INCOME (mining|staking|interest|airdrop|reward): recognize MANY pending inbounds as ordinary income at their auto\-FMV (the daily\-close market value at receipt) in one confirmed batch, with a UNIFORM `\-\-kind` + `\-\-business` flag. Shows a preview surfacing the total income recognized + the count of inbounds EXCLUDED because no price was available for their date (those stay pending — an income row with no FMV would year\-gate). Each is a voidable decision; for a single deposit use `classify\-inbound\-income`
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-kind\fR \fI<KIND>\fR
Income kind for the whole batch: mining|staking|interest|airdrop|reward
.TP
\fB\-\-business\fR
Whether this income is from a trade or business (true → SE\-tax eligible)
.TP
\fB\-\-year\fR \fI<YEAR>\fR
Restrict to a single tax year (mutually exclusive with \-\-from/\-\-to)
.TP
\fB\-\-from\fR \fI<FROM>\fR
Range start (YYYY\-MM\-DD; requires \-\-to)
.TP
\fB\-\-to\fR \fI<TO>\fR
Range end (YYYY\-MM\-DD, inclusive; requires \-\-from)
.TP
\fB\-\-wallet\fR \fI<WALLET>\fR
Only inbounds received INTO this wallet
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Print the preview and exit without writing
.TP
\fB\-\-yes\fR
Skip the interactive confirmation (non\-interactive apply)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
